reviews.reviewText: These magnetic blocks are pretty fun, especially for little ones who can’t quite stack regular blocks very high. And matching the designs that it comes with is great for the kids who can. Plus all the creative ways kids can imagine to use them. The magnets are strong enough to hold well but not so strong a toddler can’t get them apart. Great learning toy!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fun magnetic blocks!
reviews.reviewText: These blocks are so awesome! I LOVE the magnetic aspect of them. These are my son's first magnetic toys, and he's loving them! The magnets inside of the blocks shift a bit, so there's a bit of a satisfying click when they connect with other blocks. They're not super strong (the magnets), so don't hurt little fingers by pinching. But they're strong enough to stick together and be satisfying. I'd personally like the magnets a bit stronger, but the toy isn't for me, it's my son's, and they're plenty strong for him. :-)
